{"tid":2287354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有情緒病既人唔通真係好難搵到真感情？","createTime":"2020-11-15T16:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T05:11:25.000Z","uid":324823,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"727ad8e2d3e3f783b7ca0969a0d63f186b122a21","tid":2287354,"uid":324823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:19:06.000Z","msg":"一病發就好緊張就係咁chur個女仔。然後對方好似好大壓力驚左我，嚇親。<br />\n其實情緒病唔係精神病，只係情緒生病了。內心其實真係身不由己好唔開心。哩種感覺，只有同路人先明。身邊既人叫我睇開啲，無事既，對我黎講只係廢話，因為佢地就係唔明白先咁講。<br />\n而社會上，追女上，識新朋友上，總係唔敢同人講自己有病，到真係爆左出黎，上司老闆會炒您（對上份工係)，自己追女仔對對方太chur嚇走左。<br />\n其實，情緒病人，真係好需要人陪住，因為佢地內心係非常孤獨。"},{"pid":"baa2f5426c3f735ec03ba1c251452053bfaf8182","tid":2287354,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5cadf82527668e98c5b20650b5df18694dfd4b","tid":2287354,"uid":31572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:28:12.000Z","msg":"係，所以快啲好返ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(同緊自己講)"},{"pid":"de4e73edb22945aa07e82f8e04ea4eb109eb8437","tid":2287354,"uid":180390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"有冇食藥？"},{"pid":"26d41bfe95859d48a4eb3491958cf56d5db0a2eb","tid":2287354,"uid":324823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de4e73edb22945aa07e82f8e04ea4eb109eb8437","tid":2287354,"uid":180390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"有冇食藥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"食緊，食左兩年半"},{"pid":"9ce20ad29cbf7c10cd15c6e5e2f02dde130fafa5","tid":2287354,"uid":262093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"所以一早放棄追人，同人哋關係一好就會時不時暗示呢點等對方唔好鍾意自己"},{"pid":"5320bdea261601d7e529e7844b15caf6bd5b669c","